text: Ivan Pavlovsky (born 2 December 1976) is a Belarusian gymnast. He competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belarus Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Grodno
